ARTICLE 2 — SCOPE — WHAT IS AND IS NOT COVERED
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

2.1  COVERED WORK. This Agreement applies exclusively to the Covered Work as
     defined in Article 1.2. All intellectual property rights in the Covered
     Work are owned exclusively by Korlu Solutions Digitales inc.

2.2  THIRD-PARTY SOFTWARE EXCLUSION. This Agreement does not apply to, does
     not restrict, and does not claim ownership over any Third-Party Software.
     Third-Party Software incorporated into or referenced by this repository
     remains the property of its respective authors or rights holders and is
     subject exclusively to its own applicable license terms. The presence of
     Third-Party Software in this repository does not constitute a claim of
     ownership by Licensor over such software.

2.3  MODIFICATIONS TO THIRD-PARTY SOFTWARE. Where Licensor has applied
     modifications, configurations, customizations, patches, or integrations
     to Third-Party Software, only those specific modifications and
     customizations constitute Covered Work and are protected under this
     Agreement. The underlying Third-Party Software remains subject to its
     own license.

2.4  COEXISTENCE OF LICENSES. In the event of a conflict between this
     Agreement and the license of any Third-Party Software included herein,
     the Third-Party Software's license governs with respect to that software,
     and this Agreement governs with respect to the Covered Work.

